Package org.testfx.api

Class FxAssertContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.testfx.api.FxAssertContext
  • public class FxAssertContext
extends Object
    Stores contextual information for FxAssert:
    • a NodeFinder, which defaults to FxServiceContext.getNodeFinder()
    • a CaptureSupport, which defaults to FxServiceContext.getCaptureSupport()
